I- bc calculator
# Decimal Calculations
+ (addition)
- (subsraction
* (multiplication)
^ (power)
/ (division)
E.g.: 
bc
scale=8
2^8+4*4-8/2

# Heximal to Decimal conversion and vice versa
Form HEX to DEC
ibase=16

From DEC to HEX
obase=16

Form DEC to BIN
obase=2

II- dc calculator
p : print stack
c : clear stack
f : full content of stack
q : quit
E.g.:
dc
2
8
^p
250-p

III- bash calculator
echo $((arthemtic_expression))

+  (addition)
-  (subsraction
*  (multiplication)
** (power)
/  (division)



